# Trello Integration Rule

- For any Trello task, always use the local bridge at `tools/trello-editor`.
- Do not introduce direct Trello API calls in backend/frontend app code.
- Do not create alternate Trello integration scripts when the bridge can handle the request.
- Keep Trello credentials only in `tools/trello-editor/.env` (never commit secrets).
- Before Trello operations, confirm `trello-editor` is healthy at `GET /health`.
